{"tid":807150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"MOUSE 求推介","createTime":"2018-09-05T09:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T10:21:02.000Z","uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"796763e183b879e5e2e36ac74af1cff9eaaedf8c","tid":807150,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T09:52:17.000Z","msg":"其實我只係一個普通用家，唔打機純上網文書，有左iPhone iPad之後更加少開電腦，係好間唔時先會用。用開M$ confort 4500，貪佢有線冇咁易壞，又有Forward/Backward制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://compass-ssl.microsoft.com/assets/68/44/68447714-7032-425d-a700-a42ea2d84ef1.jpg?n=mk_cm4500greyv2_large.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcompass-ssl.microsoft.com%2Fassets%2F68%2F44%2F68447714-7032-425d-a700-a42ea2d84ef1.jpg%3Fn%3Dmk_cm4500greyv2_large.jpg&h=8115e7d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知用左一年左右又壞鳩左，聯強又話冇貨，退錢算鳩數。<br />\n加上用親M$ d Mouse keyboard無論平貴有線冇線都會係保養期內壞，但聯強愈做愈西成日冇貨又要人補天價換貨(同直接買新價錢分別不大)，所以打算用下其他牌子。<br />\n<br />\n但求好揸手(我手大隻)，有forward / backward制，耐用，有線都得(只用係DESKTOP)。<br />\n<br />\n謝各位巴打。"},{"pid":"b66717b0ee9ef2def91dfaaac9510fe14640329f","tid":807150,"uid":140028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"mx master 2s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2356a75987295d54219a546dd3dabef0a21c0d7a","tid":807150,"uid":4655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66717b0ee9ef2def91dfaaac9510fe14640329f","tid":807150,"uid":140028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:07:22.000Z","msg":"mx master 2s <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T10:21:02.000Z","msg":"正野喎，但係好似太貴...."}]}